3.1. Subjects, Scenarios, Instructions Data collection will proceed as described in Shriberg et al.1992 \[16\] with the following exceptions: (1) updated versions of the SRI Template Matcher and recognizer will be used; (2) subjects will use a new data collection facility (the room is smaller and has no window but is acoustically similar to the room used previously); (3) the scenarios to be solved have unique solutions; (4) the debriefing questionnalre will be a merged version of the questions used on debriefing questionnaires at SRI and at MIT in separate experiments; and (5) each subject will solve two scenarios, one using the SRI SLS and one using the SRI/MIT hybrid SLS.
